students were able to gain from Grade 3 to Grade 6 – and makes it nearly impossible to close the
achievement gap with the State average by high school graduation. It also comes at a crucial time, just
before the transition to high school.
The detailed results in the full mini-report are available here. Academic velocity findings at each
